# Production build env for the standalone lab page (naufal-lab.pages.dev).
# When the remote is embedded in the host, the host passes the party host via
# opts; this is only for the lab's OWN standalone page. Hostname only, no
# protocol (PartySocket upgrades to wss:// on an HTTPS page).
VITE_PARTY_HOST=naufal-party.yoesran.partykit.dev
